%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor COE as CoE Head

participant UI as CoE Closure Review UI
participant BFF as Project Closure BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant CLS as Project Closure Service
participant NS as Notification Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}

COE->>UI: Open CoE closure queue item
UI->>BFF: Load closure request
BFF->>ORCH: Get CoE review detail
ORCH->>CLS: Fetch closure review view
CLS->>READDB: Read project_closure, project_closure_checklist_response, <br/>project_closure_review
READDB-->>CLS: Closure review detail
CLS-->>ORCH: Review response
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show PM-submitted closure in read-only mode

alt CoE Approves
    COE->>UI: Approve closure
    UI->>BFF: Submit CoE approval
    BFF->>ORCH: Start CoE approval flow
    ORCH->>CLS: Approve closure to Governance stage
    CLS->>PRIMARYDB: Insert project_closure_review (COE approve)
    CLS->>PRIMARYDB: Update project_closure <br/>(status = Submitted for Governance Review)
    CLS->>PRIMARYDB: Insert project_closure_status_history
    PRIMARYDB-->>CLS: Save success
    CLS-->>ORCH: CoE approval success
    ORCH->>NS: Notify Governance Head
    ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish ClosureSubmittedToGovernance Event
    ORCH-->>BFF: Success
    BFF-->>UI: Show submitted for <br/>Governance review state
else CoE Sends Back
    COE->>UI: Send Back closure
    UI->>BFF: Submit send back
    BFF->>ORCH: Start CoE send back flow
    ORCH->>CLS: Return closure to PM
    CLS->>PRIMARYDB: Insert project_closure_review (COE send back)
    CLS->>PRIMARYDB: Update project_closure (status = Sent Back)
    CLS->>PRIMARYDB: Insert project_closure_status_history
    PRIMARYDB-->>CLS: Save success
    CLS-->>ORCH: Send back success
    ORCH->>NS: Notify Project Manager
    ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish ClosureSentBackByCoE Event
    ORCH-->>BFF: Success
    BFF-->>UI: Show sent back state
end
